pcmOpSubscriptionCalcQuote

Componentfm_subscription
Visibilitypublic
Transactionrequires_new

Description

The pcmOpSubscriptionCalcQuote operation returns the balance impacts that would result from purchasing the input customer level and service level deals. The purchases are only calculated, not committed to the system. Upon failure, validation errors may be returned. The quote calculation is based on a specific customer, not only on the specified pricing. In the case of a new customer, the balance impacts will be returned as if pcmOpCustCommitCustomer had been called. In the case of an existing customer, the balance impacts will be returned as if pcmOpSubscriptionPurchaseDeal had been called for each of the specified deals. In case the existing customer does not own the specified service, the result will be as if pcmOpCustModifyCustomer had been called to create the service. In case the existing customer account is inactive, the results will still be returned as if the account had been reactivated using pcmOpCustSetStatus.
